{"type": "article", "id": 16361, "title": "Pètra水壶", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-21T06:58:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135545i3FnhS1VkReqzQdO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这块像鹅卵石一样的水壶是对古阿拉伯陶器佩特拉（Pètra）的重新阐释，它们最初用来保存珍贵的液体，比如油和水，后来传入西西里，称为“Bummulo Malandrino”。液体从底部注入，然后从上面的小孔倒出来。佩特拉圆润的造型拥有舒适的手感，是结合文化传统的物品。售价 80 欧，可选有光泽或无光泽两种，<a href=\"http://improntabarre.bigcartel.com/product/petra\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143645ou1lgwcU0EYsAfm8.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143645E71aNV6pQjOMuwSU.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143646ABnE8rkYlX5U7qbd.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143646Q9AZNxO7iqyvpCnX.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}